{"tid":2506429,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女生承認非法集結罪 官令還柙拒索感化或服務令報告","createTime":"2021-04-27T10:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T11:08:07.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c938fe8287b5d4ab99cfb59ff5ce16a08ec7ada0","tid":2506429,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:04:19.000Z","msg":"市民前年10月中旬發起「神獸罷鷲」行動，抗議政府強推蒙面法。200名示威者在牛頭角港鐵站外堵路，警方拘捕多人，其中一名17歲女生今在觀塘裁判法院承認參與非法集結罪。辯方求情稱，女生立志成為產品設計師，因受社會氣氛及朋友影響才犯案，即使被捕後仍沒自暴自棄，繼續報讀日本大學課程，希望實現升學及從事設計師的夢想。惟裁判官<span class=\"red\">鍾明新</span>最終下令將女生收柙候判。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又呈上被告、被告雙親及中學校監等人所寫的求情信，他們均讚賞被告為人孝順，性格溫純善良，熱受創作，尊師重道，希望裁判官能給予被告機會，走過人生低谷，繼續升學。<br />\n<br />\n惟裁判官僅同意索閱被告的背景及<span class=\"red\">更生中心報告</span>。案件押後至下月10日判刑，其間被告須還柙候判。"},{"pid":"8377ef9bb525f2ce4c4ad4197e64b663bc29a11c","tid":2506429,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:04:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/OFJQAOGL3NFYPOR76RKJNEMXBY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FOFJQAOGL3NFYPOR76RKJNEMXBY%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oMQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=25469af5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FOFJQAOGL3NFYPOR76RKJNEMXBY%2F&h=550ab78d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/OFJQAOGL3NFYPOR76RKJNEMXBY/</a>"},{"pid":"123f230838067616a09e9fc60233fa2f24fe839f","tid":2506429,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:05:42.000Z","msg":"你感化/社會服務令 陣上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd617c3d4c28df4953a8a6bf61cbddc70b91a2f3","tid":2506429,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"123f230838067616a09e9fc60233fa2f24fe839f","tid":2506429,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:05:42.000Z","msg":"你感化/社會服務令 陣上訴<img src=\"/assets/f